01:06:55.960 --> 01:06:57.920
Medituji o Šrí Guruovi,

01:06:58.400 --> 01:07:01.040
o slabice "gu", která ukazuje stav nad

01:07:01.440 --> 01:07:04.040
třemi gunami a o slabice "ru", která ukazuje

01:07:04.400 --> 01:07:06.720
